item.dc:creator: @Zzz_O_zzZ Zzz O zzZ
item.description:
@Zzz_O_zzZ wrote:

That’s hybridScape. It has no special features on it. But all you do is put in username and pass or press login.

To log into a real server…you have to change the server by going to file and typing in the server from “server advertisement”. The port will usually always be 43594 (default, so just leave it be)

Most people have ham to get onto their server…theere are a lot of tuts around in tut section on accessing ham servers.
